<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ص خ خ:</span> <span class="c2">(الصَّاخَّةُ)</span> الصَّيْحَةُ تُصِمُّ لِشِدَّتِهَا تَقُولُ: <span class="c2">(صَخَّ)</span> الصَّوْتُ الْأُذُنَ مِنْ بَابِ رَدَّ وَمِنْهُ سُمِّيَتِ الْقِيَامَةُ <span class="c2">(الصَّاخَّةَ)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>